Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:16.14,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I wonder what it's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:17.26,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:23.72,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Isn't that the spot {\i1}you{\i0} cleaned, Kathrina?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:24.62,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:25.83,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:31.38,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Wha— Is it telling me to redo it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:34.14,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,How dare you, you little rodent!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:37.29,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,You'd better do what Dugong says.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:40.08,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Dugong is famous for having a certain jinx.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:41.14,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,A jinx?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:47.11,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Any actor that Dugong takes \Na liking to becomes a Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:54.77,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Dugong-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.07,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,You're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:00:59.87,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Come right on over to... Kokona's lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:00.72,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:02.20,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Can you be any more obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:08.61,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,Good day, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:18.89,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,Hello, Dugong-san. You're \Nstill as cute as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:24.09,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Well played, lead runner in the race \Nto become the next SIRIUS Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.30,0:01:26.48,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Dugong's completely under her spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.23,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, Yae-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:30.83,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,She's as beautiful as a painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:33.97,Main,Katrina,0,0,0,,It's just some rodent. Just you watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.23,0:01:40.24,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.24,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,You poor fool, Kathrin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:51.13,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Say goodbye to your dreams \Nof becoming a Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:55.39,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I need you all at the rehearsal hall, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.87,0:01:58.04,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,We've decided the cast \Nfor our next production.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:00.73,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Our next production?
