Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:40.58,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Our story takes place in a desert city \Nin the Middle Ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:46.07,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,We will be focusing on one of the most \Nprominent stories from {\i1}Arabian Nights{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:49.02,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,"Aladdin and the Enchanted Lamp."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.80,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,That's a pretty flashy piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:57.38,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,She said they've decided the cast already. \NAre they not doing auditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:04:01.00,Main,Terahara,0,0,0,,At SIRIUS, the sponsor and \Ndirector decide on the cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:05.75,Main,Kamiyashiki,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san used to always play the \Nlead. Now, it's usually Yae.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:11.74,Main,Terahara,0,0,0,,Ever since Hiiragi-san retired, people say \Nthat SIRIUS is a troupe without a Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:15.59,Main,Kamiyashiki,0,0,0,,SIRIUS's current objective \Nis to make Yae a Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:18.41,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Then what was the point in auditioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:21.71,Main,Terahara,0,0,0,,If you feel overlooked, \Nprove you're better than her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.15,Main,Terahara,0,0,0,,That's what we're all trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:27.04,Main,Kamiyashiki,0,0,0,,Our primary goal right now is to have \Npeople talking about SIRIUS way more
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:28.44,Main,Kamiyashiki,0,0,0,,than when Hiiragi-san was in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.63,Main,Terahara,0,0,0,,Yae-chan has the Sense and \Npopularity to do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:35.42,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Why did Hiiragi-san retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.66,Main,Terahara,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard, Kokona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:41.03,Main,Terahara,0,0,0,,You can only be on stage with \NSIRIUS until you're 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:42.76,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.93,Main,Kamiyashiki,0,0,0,,That's what Shamo-san decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.64,Main,Kamiyashiki,0,0,0,,She said it's not good to be \Nstuck in one place for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.49,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,What should I do, Shizuka-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.50,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I only have seven years left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.88,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Well, bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:56.03,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Let's make you a World Dai Star by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:57.24,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:04:59.73,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Pipe down over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.48,Main,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,Sorry!
