Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.32,Main - Italics,Shizuka,0,0,0,,give Kokona a role \Nwhere she'll stand out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:46.12,Main - Italics,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have to learn magic.
