Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.45,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,The lead role of Aladdin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.57,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,will go to Kokona Otori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:54.69,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.14,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Next, the Genie of the Lamp...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:05:59.96,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Yae Niizuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:02.11,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:03.55,Main,Troupe,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.01,Main,Troupe,0,0,0,,A newbie is playing the lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.70,Main,Troupe,0,0,0,,Yae's playing the Genie? \NThat doesn't seem to fit at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.36,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,The Royal Princess, Leila...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:11.43,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Chisa Sasuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:14.77,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,But I wanted to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.05,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,The Sultan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:17.36,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Kathrina Griebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:18.86,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What? The Sultan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:19.90,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.50,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:24.40,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Aladdin's nemesis, Abdullah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.77,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Panda Yanagiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:27.49,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,P-Please wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.15,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.86,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Niizumacchi's playing the Genie? \NI mean, that's one thing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:33.99,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,A newbie's playing Aladdin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.16,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,That's inconceivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:41.78,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,This was decided after careful discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:43.27,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:57.07,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I-I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:07:00.06,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'll make sure this play is a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:01.70,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Please let me do the part!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.73,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I'll do my best, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.13,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,All right.
