Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.45,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,This is your big break, Kokona!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:30.08,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. I need to do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.62,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,So that Panda-chan and the \Nothers acknowledge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:33.88,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,And the audience...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:38.61,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,And for yourself! You're one step \Ncloser to becoming a Dai Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:40.94,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.35,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,May I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.01,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Uh, yes!
