Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:54.20,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,From now until the production is over,\N you'll be following that regimen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.61,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,You need to get the fundamentals of \Nstage acting down once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.42,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,The fundamentals of stage acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:02.28,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.99,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Right now, you don't have \Nthe stamina or talent
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:08.04,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,to be up on stage for 90 minutes\N in the lead role.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:12.48,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Then why did you pick Kokona \Nfor the lead role?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.59,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,For SIRIUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:22.55,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,No part-time jobs \Nuntil after the final show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:25.19,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,SIRIUS will make sure you're \Ntaken care of in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.86,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Glance through that regimen by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.98,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,What does she mean that it's for SIRIUS?
