Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:49.80,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.32,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,This definitely doesn't seem \Nlike it's from Kathrina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.09,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.59,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:08.91,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. You don't need to be so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:10.47,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:12.98,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Th-These are...
