Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:17.75,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Scripts from past productions of {\i1}Arabian \NNights{\i0} our senpais at SIRIUS performed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:20.76,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,They're from my secret SIRIUS collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.88,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Our senpais wrote in a whole bunch of notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:26.05,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,I figured they might help \Nyou understand your role.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.38,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I can borrow these?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.61,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:32.31,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san chose you, and you said you \Nwere going to see the role through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:36.50,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,So I've... made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.26,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being so rude earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.15,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Panda-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.30,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Let's make this production a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:57.77,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'll do my best.
