Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.30,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:22.32,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,These notes suggest that everyone had \Na hard time getting this role down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.55,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:27.06,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,A manly Aladdin, a timid \Nand unreliable Aladdin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.31,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord6\shad0\blur6\fs51\c&H7178BF&\3c&HD8EDF8&\b1\fax-0.15\frz359.7\pos(1335,348)}Even though you're surprised by Genie, make sure\N you don't forget the excitement of something starting!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.06,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord6\shad0\blur6\fs60\c&H563A3F&\3c&HDCE2EA&\b1\frz359.7\pos(1623,414)}Genie: Ah!
