Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:32.06,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord6\shad0\blur6\fs60\c&H563A3F&\3c&HCFD9E6&\b1frz359.7}...merchants...\N...don't look down.\NThey're so busy running their shops...\NNo one even sees me...\NNo one even knows my name...\NThe apple I stole from the merchant...\NWho...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:31.62,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,An Aladdin whose life in the grueling \Ndesert has made him detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.24,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,They're all completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:38.01,Main,Kathrin,0,0,0,,That just means the character \Nof Aladdin lacks any core.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:38.97,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Core?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:41.43,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,The roles of the Genie, \NAbdullah, and Princess Leila
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:44.46,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,are all written out in great \Ndetail in the scripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:48.08,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord6\shad0\blur6\fs60\c&H563A3F&\3c&HCFD9E6&\b1\frz359.7}Aladdin: Everyone's desperate to survive.\NAt night, they all get drunk to the music.\NYou can smell the sweet aroma and hear the laughter...\NSee? It's starting again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:48.08,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord6\shad0\blur6\fs54\c&H563A3F&\3c&HCFD9E6&\b1\frz359.7\fax-0.15\pos(1890,51)}Say each of \Nthese sentences clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:48.04,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,But there's no solid direction for Aladdin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:51.10,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Which means his character takes a lot \Nfrom the actor's personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:51.08,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord6\shad0\blur6\fs60\c&H563A3F&\3c&HCFD9E6&\b1\frz359.7}Aladdin: ~Sings~\NI love this city!\NEveryone's desperate to survive.\NAt night, they all get drunk to the music.\NYou can smell the sweet aroma and hear the laughter...\NSee? It's starting again tonight.\N~Sings~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:51.08,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord6\shad0\blur6\fs54\c&H7178BF&\3c&HCFD9E6&\b1\frz359.7\fax-0.15\pos(1890,51)}Make sure your body...\NDon't let this line get drowned out. \NIt's important
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.04,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,At least, that's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:55.03,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,The actor's personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:59.08,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,With that in mind, it's really easy to \Nimagine how Niizuma would play Aladdin.
