Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.67,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Yae-chan's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:05.83,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,That alone is enough to bring \Nher characters to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:10.51,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,The audience will surely enter the world \Nof {\i1}Arabian Nights{\i0} through Yae-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:14.11,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What makes Niizuma scary isn't \Njust her singing Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:17.14,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Her ability to make each character \Nfeel like they're actually her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:20.50,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I hate to admit it, but I don't \Nhave that kind of charm right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:25.41,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of Aladdin \NI should try to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:28.55,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,We'll just have to try out various versions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:30.41,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:35.53,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You'll need someone to \Npractice with, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.13,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Uh, hello? I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.35,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Well, three's always better than two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:44.25,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,You're going to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:46.72,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,If you end up messing up this role,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.84,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'll seem like a failure, too, \Nsince you got the role instead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:54.34,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,More importantly, if you don't do this \Nrole properly, I'm going to upstage you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:56.46,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,As the Sultan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:59.18,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I think that itself could ruin the play...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:01.76,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,And that's exactly why you \Nhave to work hard, Kokona!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.06,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.25,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yae-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:11.33,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What are you doing here at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.94,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Didn't Hiiragi-san tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.13,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Tell us what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:20.39,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I'm going to be living with Kokona-san \Nuntil the production starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:21.02,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.09,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:23.80,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Living with...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:27.55,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I look forward to our time \Ntogether, Kokona-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:30.81,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Or rather... Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:37.93,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,1)\fnArial\shad0\b1\frx-5\bord0\fs108\c&H8A62FD&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(964.368,386.907)}S{\c&HF9AA06&}t{\c&H30C2FF&}e{\c&H8A62FD&}l{\c&HF9AA06&}l{\c&H30C2FF&}a {\c&H8A62FD&}o{\c&HF9AA06&}f{\c&H30C2FF&} t{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e {\c&H30C2FF&}T{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}a{\c&H8A62FD&}t{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}r{\c&H8A62FD&}:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:42.22,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,"Dear Kokona Otori-sama."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:45.29,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,"I heard that you've agreed \Nto take care of our Yae
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.95,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,in order to help her prepare for her role.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:53.95,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I do apologize that we are greeting you \Nby letter rather than properly in person."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:58.71,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,"Ever since she was little, our daughter was \Nvery aware of her surroundings,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:56.86,Main - Top,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Would you like me to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:59.71,Main - Top,Kokona,0,0,0,,N-No! Yae-chan, you can \Njust make yourself at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.09,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,filled with compassion,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:05.04,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,determined and uncompromising once \Nshe sets her mind on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.70,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Everyone often compliments her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:10.73,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,saying that she's an absolute gem, \Nbut sometimes this is not the case..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.09,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Isn't this overly long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:16.19,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I mean... I can tell that your parents love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.69,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But what's this about \Npreparing for your role?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:21.35,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Yes. Aladdin and the Genie go through
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:25.06,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,good times and bad together after they meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:31.36,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I thought it was necessary to be in sync \Nwith Kokona-san, who's playing Aladdin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:35.03,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I did actually tell Hiiragi-san \Nabout this earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:36.32,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.39,Main,Kudo,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:39.33,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.10,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.08,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,More importantly, about this part...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:47.62,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I would've cleaned up if she'd told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:51.23,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,So, yes. From today until \Nthe production starts,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:54.83,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,as the Genie that serves Kokona-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:57.39,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I would like to take care of you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.47,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,M-Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:02.24,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Wait a second! You're planning \Nto stay in this room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:05.11,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,It's cramped enough with Shizuka here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.40,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,I heard everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:12.70,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Why do you two {\i1}always{\i0} \Nshow up at times like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.74,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,The walls are paper thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.78,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,We'll take real good care of Kathrin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:17.40,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:23.57,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Next, we're going to \Ninvestigate Kathrin's Sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:27.75,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Hey! No! Your room's sorta scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:30.18,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,K-K-Kokona!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:35.26,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Maybe we should've stopped them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:38.47,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Let's treat Kathrina to some \Nice cream sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:40.62,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.40,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,Your wish is my command, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:51.05,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,I shall grant you any wish at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:54.24,Main,Yae,0,0,0,,If it is within my power, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.79,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Let us savor this happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:58.68,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.55,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,Good morning, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:19.43,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yae-chan? Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:22.82,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,I'm the Genie! Now, time for \Nyour morning rehearsal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.51,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,Let's give it our all today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.21,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.17,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Were you able to meet your quota?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:38.24,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yes, I made it. Three kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:40.72,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I see. In that case, hop \Nright into vocal training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.01,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Tongue twisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:43.33,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.71,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,She's a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.49,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.31,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:54.98,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,An assignment from Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:58.09,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I have to do a scene as a different\N character each morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:01.60,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is Macbeth. \NThe day after that, Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:04.77,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,After that, there's Jekyll, \NHyde, Inspector Javert...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:06.80,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,All male roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.40,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:14.42,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I-I mean... if you need someone to read \Nwith you, I guess I wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:18.00,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Really?! It starts with Act 3, Scene 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:27.01,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Don't sit pigeon-toed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.62,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Separate those feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:29.75,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:32.63,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,When playing a male character, \Nyou'll use big gestures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.34,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Focus power in your fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:36.38,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Think about every movement you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:37.42,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.27,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,In the morning, I have to work \Nout and practice the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:46.42,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,In the afternoon, I have a table read,\N then singing and dance lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:49.78,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,At night, I have a one-on-one \Nwith Hiiragi-sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:56.06,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,This is going to continue \Nfor three months?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.63,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, Dugong-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:05.10,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Did you come to cheer me... up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:12.83,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:15.43,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,Welcome back, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.31,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,Your futon has been laid out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:19.37,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Whoa, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:22.88,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um... I just can't get used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:25.50,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Could you just call me Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.98,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,Well, that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:30.48,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,I could've sworn my master's \Nname was Aladdin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.54,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,That's Yae-chan for you... \NShe's not breaking character.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:38.53,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I'm kidding. If you so desire, \NI'll stop for today, Kokona-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:43.28,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,You did amazing work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:45.36,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,What an absolute gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:47.29,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:51.54,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Am I really going to make it, \Npracticing like this every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:54.19,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Is this training difficult for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:56.67,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Not exactly, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:59.45,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I know the fundamentals are important...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:02.52,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But you've had no time \Nto prepare for your role.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:06.32,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I've been trying to figure out a bunch of \Nthings while Kokona's at school, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:09.44,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,What kind of Aladdin \Nshould I be playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.31,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:12.48,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,There's still time before the production.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.48,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,You don't need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.68,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.82,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Yes! Not to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:21.12,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,The Aladdin you should play is quite obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.37,Main,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:27.53,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Aladdin meets the Genie, and ends up \Ntrusting him because of how devoted he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:29.73,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,It's not because he can use magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:35.41,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,but because Aladdin has spent all his \Nlife trying to survive in a desert city,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:38.55,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,and the Genie is the first \Nfriend that he can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:44.39,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Can you trust me, Kokona-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.15,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yes... I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:48.79,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Then it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:52.13,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,That's exactly how you should \Npursue the role of Aladdin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.35,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:59.61,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I'm sure this production will go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:01.15,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:04.27,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,If I'm with you, Yae-chan, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:07.95,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:33.15,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,Here you go, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.08,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:43.76,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yae-chan, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:44.78,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:49.07,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Why are you playing the Genie \Ninstead of the lead role?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:52.37,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,If I want to become a Dai Star,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:55.54,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I need to show everyone a new Yae Niizuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.98,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,A new you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:19:58.77,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:03.86,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Innocent and pure maidens like the \NLittle Mermaid and Princess Kaguya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:08.25,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I thought those were the kinds of \Ncharacters people wanted from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:09.92,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:12.60,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I realized that I couldn't get closer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:15.87,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,to becoming a Dai Star by only playing \Nthe roles people wanted from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:18.94,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,So you're working to become a Dai Star, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:20.37,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.21,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs96\bord6\shad6\fnArial\c&HA3AAAB&\3c&H2F3035&\b1\blur12\pos(1638,216)}Arabian
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:37.11,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,The poster came out quite nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:38.07,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:41.00,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,First, I'll become a Dai Star at SIRIUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:43.15,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Then, a World Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:45.95,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,And then, finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.27,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Finally?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:54.48,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36\bord6\shad0\fnArial\c&HA3AAAB&\3c&H2F3035&\b1\blur6\pos(963,273)}Arabian Nights
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:50.55,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:54.47,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Is it really okay for me to play the lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.76,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,What if I really mess up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.31,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:00.49,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,I'm the Genie of the lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:04.41,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,You just need to tell me \Nwhat you wish for, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:06.35,Main,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,And then, I'll make it come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.51,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Then I have two wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:16.87,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I wish for this production to \Nbe a success. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:20.35,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I wish for you to \Nbecome a Dai Star, Yae-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:22.58,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.92,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,A very lovely wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:43.62,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You're not going to sleep yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:44.47,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:47.58,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Something still doesn't sit right with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:50.16,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Why was Koko-chan chosen for the lead role?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:53.43,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Oh... I get it now.
